abstract: Some executives at small companies have reservations about President Trump, but also concerns about Bernie Sanders and Elizabeth Warren.
snippet: Some executives at small companies have reservations about President Trump, but also concerns about Bernie Sanders and Elizabeth Warren.
lead_paragraph: When it comes to President Trump’s economic policies, there is not much that appeals to Grady Cope, the founder of a machining and assembly company in Englewood, Colo.

abstract: A campaign is underway to get the British Parliament’s great bell to ring when the country leaves the E.U. on Jan. 31. But there are hurdles: the cost and repairs.
snippet: A campaign is underway to get the British Parliament’s great bell to ring when the country leaves the E.U. on Jan. 31. But there are hurdles: the cost and repairs.
lead_paragraph: LONDON — When Britain leaves the European Union at the end of the month, it must secure trade ties to the Continent, revamp its migration rules and reset relations with global partners like the United States, to name just a few looming challenges.

snippet: The last Democratic debate before the Iowa caucuses had high stakes — and low drama.
lead_paragraph: Four Democratic primary candidates locked in a near tie in Iowa. Less than three weeks until the caucuses there. And the looming spectacle of a contentious impeachment trial against a president running for re-election.
